CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 23, 1953, pg. 10 reads: "Women Of The Year - These three prominent Pittsburgh women along with one who isn't pictured, were named "Women of the Year" by Pi Chapter of Iota Phi Lambda Sorority last Friday at a luncheon at the Greene Hearthe. Left to right, Mrs. Lois Lee Dorsey, Mrs. Hazel Garland and Miss Martha Tyson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: "Women of the Year" winners Lois Lee Dorsey, Hazel Garland, and Martha Tyson standing in the Greene Hearth for Iota Phi Lambda luncheon, another version
